show.title: Bachpan ka Pyaar
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/eCcWeG
show.description: Aarav and Preeti were married as kids but got separated when her family moved away. 15 years later, they unknowingly meet again at work — neither recognizing the other. As they fall in love, both keep searching for the childhood partner they once married, unaware they’ve already found each other.
